EN: This is a waste of time activity, I'm not interested.

ZH: 不要浪费机会，抓住每一个可以学习的机会。
EN: Don't waste opportunities, seize every chance to learn.

ZH: 他总是浪费自己的才华，没有做出任何成就。
EN: He always wastes his talent and hasn't achieved anything.

